<i>noun</i>: 폐점 [폐ː점/페ː점], 폐업 [폐ː업/페ː업] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폐점 [폐ː점/페ː점]</dt><br>
<dd>1. closure; closedown</dd><br>
<dd>영업을 그만두거나 망해서 가게가 더 이상 운영되지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a shop or store going out of business and stopping operation.</dd><br>
<dd>2. closing for the day</dd><br>
<dd>가게의 하루 영업이 끝남.</dd><br>
<dd>The day's operation of a shop or store ending.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폐업 [폐ː업/페ː업]</dt><br>
<dd>closure; cessation of business</dd><br>
<dd>영업을 그만둠.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of closing one's business.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>